      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence study — GCI assessment",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (coarse 2.1 M, medium 5.8 M, fine 14.2 M cells). Grid Convergence Index on NIH: GCI_fine = 3.9 %. Asymptotic range confirmed (ratio = 1.02). Discretization error factor assessed at Gradation 2 against required Gradation 3.",
      "validationMetric": "GCI",
      "metricValue": 3.9,
      "acceptanceBand": 5.0,
      "passed": true
    }
  ],
  "hasCredibilityFactor": [
