      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2) holds ISO 9001 certification. However, the regression test suite does not include the power-law non-Newtonian viscosity model activated for blood rheology. A gap at level 3 vs. required level 4 is recorded."
