      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) or equivalent must be demonstrated for the hemolysis transport scalar equation at the spatial order of accuracy used in production runs.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not for the user-defined scalar transport equation implementing the hemolysis damage model. Achieved level 3; required level 4."
    },
