      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental conditions must be measured and reported with calibrated instrumentation traceable to NIST standards; temperature and hematocrit must be controlled within ±1 °C and ±1 % respectively.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments used a recirculating loop with temperature control to ±1.5 °C, slightly exceeding the ±1 °C requirement. Hematocrit controlled to ±1 %. Achieved level 2; required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
