      "rationale": "Residuals converged 4 orders of magnitude; mass imbalance 0.008 %. Convergence criterion of 5 orders not fully met for the scalar hemolysis transport equation in two of five operating points. Achieved level 2; required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
