      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "The constitutive hemolysis model must be validated against mechanistic data across the shear-stress and exposure-time space relevant to the COU; alternative model forms must be evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used. Literature review identified three alternative model forms; only one (Arora et al.) was evaluated. Shear-stress space coverage in validation data is 60 % of COU operating range. Achieved level 3; required level 5."
