      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary conditions must be sourced from peer-reviewed literature or direct measurement; uncertainty bounds must be assigned to all inputs.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity sourced from Merrill et al. (1965) with ±12 % uncertainty. Inlet velocity profile derived from 2D Doppler ultrasound with ±8 % uncertainty. Rotor clearance from manufacturing tolerance specification. One input (red blood cell deformability index) lacks a published uncertainty bound. Achieved level 3; required level 4."
