      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs must be demonstrated quantitatively for all primary boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "Factor not assessed. The validation experiment used bovine blood at hematocrit 33 %; the COU specifies human blood at hematocrit 38–45 %. A formal equivalency argument bridging animal-to-human blood rheology was not documented. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
